Matthew M. Gosling 
Executive Compensation
As Senior Vice President and General Counsel at DEPOMED INC, Matthew M. Gosling  made $2,022,447 in total compensation.  Of this total $441,577 was received as a salary, $268,637 was received as a bonus, $585,047 was received in stock options, $718,500 was awarded as stock and $8,686 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2015 fiscal year. 


