Matthew Gosling | Management | Depomed





















Matthew M. GoslingSenior Vice President and General Counsel
Mr. Gosling joined Depomed in June 2006 as vice president and general counsel. Prior to joining Depomed, he was a partner at the law firm of Heller Ehrman, where he practiced in the corporate and securities group for nine years. Mr. Gosling received a J.D. degree from the University of Chicago and a B.A. degree from Trinity University.




