Matthew M. Gosling's Biography




			Matthew M. Gosling has served as Senior Vice President and General Counsel since January 2011 and Vice President and General Counsel since June 2006. Prior to joining the Company, Mr. Gosling was a partner of Heller Ehrman LLP, an international law firm. Mr. Gosling holds a B.A. from Trinity University and a J.D. from the University of Chicago.
		
